sider.com%2Fmom-spent-1200-olivia-rodrigo-tickets-guts-world-tour-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epending%20this%20much%20money%20on%20my%20young%20daughter%3C%2Fa%3E's%20birthday%20or%20Christmas%20present%2C%20there%20was%20another%20part%20of%20me%20that%20knew%20this%20was%20a%20chance%20for%20connection%20between%20us.%20During%20those%20years%2C%20she%20started%20wearing%20contact%20lenses%2C%20grew%20her%20hair%20long%2C%20began%20shaving%20her%20legs%2C%20made%20the%20duck%20face%20in%20photos%2C%20and%20was%20changing%20as%20young%20teenage%20girls%20do.%20And%20it%20felt%20like%20it%20all%20happened%20overnight.%20When%20I%20look%20at%20photos%20from%20these%20two%20concerts%2C%20I%20can%20see%20the%20changes.%20She%20goes%20from%20looking%20cute%20to%20pretty%20and%20from%20silly%20to%20self-aware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Swift's%20Reputation%20Tour%20in%202018%20happened%20around%20my%20daughter's%20sophomore%20year%20of%20high%20school%20and%20three%20years%20since%20the%20last%20tour.%20When%20I%20asked%20her%20if%20she%20wanted%20to%20get%20tickets%2C%20she%20said%20she%20didn't%20like%20the%20album.%20Again%2C%20things%20were%20changing.%20I%20don't%20know%20why%20she%20didn't%20like%20the%20new%20album.%20She%20was%20broadening%20her%20musical%20taste%2C%20perhaps.%20She%20preferred%20going%20to%20concerts%20featuring%20Wiz%20Khalifa%2C%20Travis%20Scott%2C%20and%20the%20Chainsmokers.%20And%20she%20most%20definitely%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20with%20me.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221094c1c5-f19d-48d9-9c4d-a1cea3e41062%5C%22%3EI%20missed%20my%20Taylor%20Swift-loving%20daughter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20longed%20for%20my%20Taylor%20Swift-loving%20girl%20and%20wondered%20how%20I%20would%20ever%20find%20a%20connection%20with%20who%20she%20was%20becoming.%20There%20were%20smaller%2C%20cheaper%20ways%20to%20connect%20with%20my%20daughter.%20I%20read%20the%20same%20books%20she%20did%20or%20watched%20the%20same%20shows.%20But%20as%20she%20tumbled%20through%20those%20years%20and%20acquired%20the%20bumps%20and%20bruises%20of%20disappointing%20friendships%20and%20heartaches%2C%20I%20was%20not%20the%20person%20she%20wanted%20to%20bandage%20her%20wounds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20fights%20were%20mostly%20about%20her%20wanting%20to%20do%20something%20that%20I%20didn't%20think%20she%20was%20ready%20to%20do.%20Whether%20it%20was%20a%20concert%20or%20a%20party%2C%20I%20was%20rarely%20ready%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Byes%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20she%20was%20always%20halfway%20out%20the%20door.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20a%20time%20she%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20a%20friend's%20house.%20For%20some%20reason%20I%20can't%20recall%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20her%20to%20go.%20I%20told%20her%20no%20and%20she%20told%20me%20she%20was%20going%20anyway.%20When%20she%20moved%20to%20walk%20past%20me%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20physically%20blocking%20her%20from%20going%20down%20our%20stairs.%20I%20stood%20folding%20my%20arms%20across%20my%20chest%20and%20my%20legs%20spread%20wider%20than%20my%20hips%2C%20knees%20slightly%20bent.%20She%20tried%20to%20get%20around%20me%20again%20and%20I%20moved%20in%20front%20of%20her.%20My%20heart%20was%20racing%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20my%20own%20behavior.%20I%20eventually%20turned%20around%20and%20walked%20away.%20I%20can't%20remember%20if%20she%20went%20or%20not.%20What%20I%20do%20remember%20vividly%20is%20how%20I%20felt%20when%20it%20was%20over.%20I%20had%20this%20horrible%20feeling%20of%20having%20lost%20control%20and%20having%20said%20or%20yelled%20unkind%20things%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20feeling%20justified%20in%20saying%20no.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20and%20daughter%20posing%20for%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccb67f1aa2ac29ee3433aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20daughter%20reconnected%20thanks%20to%20T