appy%20Meals%20and%20glow%20sticks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20packed%20the%20car%20and%20left%20around%209%20a.m.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShe%20had%20grown%20into%20her%20independence.%20And%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20our%20drive%20was%20not%20only%20better%20than%20I%20expected%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20something%20shifting.%20Susie%20drove%2C%20we%20played%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20and%20we%20talked%20about%20the%20show%20the%20night%20before.%20Together%2C%20we%20could%20appreciate%20the%20more%20mature%20and%20nuanced%20songs%20that%20Swift%20was%20singing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20smiled%20and%20sang%20to%20our%20old%20favorites%2C%20%26quot%3BMean%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-number-one-hits-songs-billboard-hot-100-chart-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENever%20Ever%20Getting%20Back%20Together.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20Those%20songs%20felt%20like%20old%20friends%20visiting%20us%20after%20a%20long%20time%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20that%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Perfectly%20Fine%26quot%3B%20is%20one%20of%20her%20favorite%20songs%20from%20many%20albums%20ago.%20This%20was%20new%20information.%20Did%20it%20remind%20her%20of%20a%20past%20crush%3F%20I%20had%20so%20many%20questions%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20not%20to%20ask%20so%20that%20we%20could%20keep%20talking.%20Nothing%20killed%20our%20conversations%20more%20than%20me%20asking%20a%20bunch%20of%20questions.%20She%20continued%20to%20share%20stories%20about%20her%20college%20life%20and%20her%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20savored%20every%20bit%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a32e71ad-3300-4b53-818f-ab26679cbd9d%5C%22%3EWe've%20all%20grown%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20about%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-paid-thousands-to-see-taylor-swift-us-europe-eras-tour-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%20had%20grown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too.%20Like%20my%20relationship%20with%20my%2