ated%20in%20the%20Arbaeen%20Walk%2C%20with%20thousands%20reaching%20Karbala.%20Along%20the%2080%20km%20route%2C%20food%2C%20drinks%2C%20medical%20services%2C%20and%20accommodation%20were%20provided%20by%20Iraqi%20locals%2C%20who%20opened%20their%20homes%20to%20the%20pilgrims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%201%2C455%20stalls%20were%20set%20up%20from%20Najaf%20to%20Karbala%2C%20where%20people%20from%20around%20the%20world%20offered%20food%20and%20drinks%20representative%20of%20their%20cultures.%20Indian%20pilgrims%20also%20set%20up%20several%20stalls%2C%20including%20Caravan-e-Hind%2C%20providing%20accommodation%2C%20food%2C%20and%20medical%20services.%20Over%2050%20Indian%20doctors%20were%20present%2C%20offering%20medical%20care%20throughout%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20reaching%20Karbala%2C%20many%20Indian%20devotees%20visited%20Imam%20Hussain's%20Shrine%20to%20offer%20their%20respects.%20In%20a%20symbolic%20gesture%2C%20they%20hoisted%20the%20Indian%20flag%2C%20which%20was%20warmly%20received%20by%20the%20local%20Iraqis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Syed%20Afzal%2C%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Hazrat%20Abbas%20Holy%20Shrine%2C%20stated%20that%20over%2021%2C000%20volunteers%20were%20mobilised%20to%20ensure%20the%20smooth%20conduct%20of%20the%20pilgrimage.%20%26quot%3BOur%20aim%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20no%20devotee%20faces%20any%20difficulty%20during%20the%20Arbaeen%20pilgrimage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fg6fpv4jg_ali_625x300_27_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20notable%20Indian%20personalities%2C%20including%20actor%20Javed%20Jaffrey%20and%20Ladakh%20MP%20Mohammad%20Hanifa%2C%20participated%20in%20this%20year's%20Arbaeen%20pi