ing%20Vadodara%20have%20witnessed%20severe%20waterlogging%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20incessant%20rain%20for%20several%20days.%20Three%20people%20have%20died%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours.%20According%20to%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20from%20Monday%20to%20Tuesday%2C%20various%20parts%20of%20Gujarat%20received%20significant%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVadodara%20received%2026%20cm%20of%20rainfall%20on%20Monday%2C%20IMD%20said.%20Apart%20from%20Vadodara%2C%20Rajkot%20received%2019%20cm%2C%20Ahmedabad%2012%20cm%2C%20Bhuj%20and%20Naliya%20received%208%20cm%2C%20Okha%20and%20Dwarka%20received%207%20cm%20while%20Porbandar%20received%205%20cm%20of%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20significant%20amount%20of%20rainfall%20observed%20from%200830%20hrs%20IST%20of%2026.08.2024%20to%200530%20hrs%20IST%20of%2027.08.2024%20(in%20cm)%3A%20Gujarat%20Region%3A%20Baroda-28%2C%20Ahemdabad-12%2C%20Surat-4%3B%20Saurashtra%20%26amp%3B%20Kutch%3A%20Rajkot-19%2C%20Bhuj-8%2C%20Naliya-8%2C%20Okha%20%26amp%3B%20Dwarka%20-7each%2C%20Porbandar-5%2C%26quot%3B%20IMD%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vishwamitri%20river%20that%20flows%20through%20Vadodara%20has%20been%20overflowing%20leading%20to%20residential%20areas%20experiencing%20severe%20waterlogging.%20People%20were%20seen%20wading%20through%20knee-deep%20waters%20and%20the%20waterlogging%20led%20to%20traffic%20snarls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20water%20from%20Ajwa%20Reservoir%20and%20Pratappura%20Reservoir%20was%20released%20into%20Vishwamitri%20River%2C%20leading%20to%20waterlogging%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20said%20that%20severe%20waterlogging%20had%20been%20experienced%20since%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWater%20has%20entered%20houses%20since%20Monday%20evening%20in%20low-lying%20areas.%20People%20are%20shifting%20to%20other%20safe%20locations.%20There%20is%20a%20shortage%20of%20food.%20People%20are%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20difficulty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResident%20said%20that%20they%20had%20never%20seen%20a%20flood-like%20situation%20like%20this%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Mahadev%20Temple%20complex%20in%20Vadodara%20was%20submerged%20due%20to%20heavy%20rainfall%20and%20the%20temple%20premises%20were%20shut%20on%20Tuesday.%20People%20said%20that%20they%20had%20never%20seen%20this%20much%20rain%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gandhinagar%20number%20plates%20of%20vehicles%20were%20found%20scattered%20at%20Mahatma%20Mandir%20Underbridge%2C%20Sector-13%20after%20the%20water%20receded.%20The%20area%20faced%20severe%20waterlogging%20due%20to%20incessant%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChief%20Minister%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20has%20held%20a%20meeting%20today%20with%20all%20the%20district%20officials%20through%20videoconference%20and%20directed%20us%20regarding%20human%20life.%20He%20directed%20us%20that%20people%20shouldn't%20face%20electricity%20shortages%2C%20medicinal%20shortages%20and%20other%20needful%20things.%20In%20the%20coming%202-3%20days%2C%20rain%20is%20expected%20as%20forecasted%20by%20the%20IMD%2C%20leaves%20of%20all%20the%20district%20collectors%20and%20concerned%20officials%20have%20been%20cancelled%20and%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20join%20the%20relief%20and%20rescue%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Gujarat%20Relief%20Commissioner%20Alok%20Kumar%20Pandey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWater%20should%20also%20be%20arranged%20wherever%20there%20is%20a%20power%20cut.%201%2C653%20people%20were%20rescued%20and%2017800%20people%20were%20shifted.%20There%20have%20been%2099%20deaths%20during%20the%20entire%20monsoon.%203%20deaths%20have%20occurred%20in%2024%20hours%2C%201%20in%20Dahod%20and%202%20in%20Gandhinagar%20district%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724740500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F20