r%20has%20resurfaced.%20The%20story%2C%20first%20shared%20by%20Kick%20Kennedy%20--%20the%20daughter%20of%20RFK%20Jr%20--%20with%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.townandcountrymag.com%2Fsociety%2Ftradition%2Fa924%2Fkick-kennedy-interview%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Ea%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sheds%20light%20on%20a%20childhood%20memory.%20According%20to%20Ms%20Kennedy%2C%20her%20father%20decapitated%20a%20whale%20carcass%20during%20a%20family%20trip%20to%20Hyannis%20Port%2C%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20gained%20traction%20recently%20after%20Ms%20Kennedy%20was%20spotted%20with%20actor%20Ben%20Affleck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20when%20RFK%20Jr%20discovered%20a%20whale%20carcass%20washed%20ashore%20on%20Squaw%20Island.%20The%20US%20politician%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20indulge%20in%20what%20his%20daughter%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpeculiar%20fascination%20with%20dead%20animals%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20a%20chainsaw%2C%20RFK%20Jr%20reportedly%20hurried%20down%20to%20the%20beach%20and%20proceeded%20to%20decapitate%20the%20whale%20on%20the%20spot.%20He%20then%20attached%20the%20massive%20head%20to%20the%20family's%20minivan%20with%20a%20bungee%20cord%2C%20determined%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20their%20home%20in%20Mount%20Kisco%2C%20New%20York%2C%20for%20further%20study.%20The%20family%20endured%20a%20five-hour%20drive%20back%2C%20with%20the%20whale's%20rotting%20remains%20emitting%20a%20stench%20that%2C%20according%20to%20Kick%20Kennedy%2C%20assaulted%20every%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20we%20accelerated%20on%20the%20highway%2C%20whale%20juice%20would%20pour%20into%20the%20windows%20of%20the%20car%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20rankest%20thing%20on%20the%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kennedy%C2%A0recalled%20in%20the%20interview.%20The%20situation%20was%20so%20unbearable%20that%20the%20family%20resorted%20to%20wearing%20plastic%20bags%20over%20their%20heads%20with%20mouth%20holes%20cut%20out%2C%20which%20brought%20out%20bewildered%20and%20disgusted%20reactions%20from%20fellow%20drivers.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20on%20the%20highway%20were%20giving%20us%20the%20finger%2C%20but%20that%20was%20just%20normal%20day-to-day%20stuff%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%C2%A0revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20whale%20beheading%20incident%20is%20disturbing%2C%20it%20was%20not%20the%20only%20such%20occurrence%20in%20the%20Kennedy%20household.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20RFK%20Jr%20admitted%20in%20a%20viral%20interview%20with%20Roseanne%20Barr%20that%20he%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F08%2F04%2Fus-news%2Frfk-jr-says-he-dumped-dead-bear-in-central-park-after-ditching-plan-to-skin-it-in-bizarre-video%2F%5C%22%3Edumped%20a%20dead%20bear%20cub%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Central%20Park%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recounted%20how%2C%20during%20a%20falconing%20trip%20in%20Goshen%2C%20New%20York%2C%20he%20discovered%20the%20cub%20after%20it%20had%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20car.%20Planning%20to%20skin%20the%20bear%20and%20use%20the%20meat%2C%20he%20placed%20it%20in%20his%20van.%20However%2C%20after%20a%20night%20of%20drinking%20with%20friends%2C%20they%20decided%20it%20would%20be%20amusing%20to%20dump%20the%20bear%20in%20Central%20Park%20and%20make%20it%20appear%20as%20though%20it%20had%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20bike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20bizarre%20stories%20resurface%2C%20the%20spotlight%20is%20also%20on%20Ms%20Kennedy%2C%20who%20has%20recently%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20company%20of%20recently%20divorced%20Ben%20Affleck%2C%2052.%20The%20two%20have%20been%20spotted%20at%20various%20hotspots%2C%20including%20the%20Polo%20Lounge%20at%20the%20Beverly%20Hills%20Hotel%2C%20leading%20to%20dating%20rumours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724739600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqnku3nn_kick-kennedy_625x300_27_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3