.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20look%20in%20to%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20organisations%2C%20icnlduing%20the%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee%20have%20demanded%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20release%20of%20the%20film%2C%20claiming%20it%20spreads%20an%20%26quot%3Banti-Sikh%26quot%3B%20narrative%2C%20and%20misrepresents%20Sikhs%20as%20%C2%A0%26quot%3Bseparatists%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie's%20trailer%20shows%20young%20Indira's%20bond%20with%20her%20father%2C%20the%20late%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20as%20she%20entered%20politics.%20It%20then%20shows%20how%20she%20dealt%20with%20conflicts%2C%20political%20turmoil%2C%20and%20other%20issues%20over%20her%20political%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724734620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fimh918pg_kangana-_625x300_18_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranaut-shares-video-of-death-threat-over-new-film-seeks-cops-help-6426438%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20MP%20and%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20on%20Tuesday%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20police%20for%20help%20after%20a%20video%20of%20a%20group%20of%20men%20threatening%20her%20over%20the%20release%20of%20her%20next%20film%20'Emergency'%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranaut-shares-video-of-death-threat-over-new-film-seeks-cops-help-6426438%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Patient%20Grabs%20Woman%20Doctor%20By%20Hair%2C%20Bangs%20Head%20At%20Andhra%20Hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20nationwide%20call%20for%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20doctors%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20a%20woman%20junior%20d