54%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Faustrian-surgeon-let-teenage-daughter-drill-hole-in-patients-skull-13203934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Austrian%20surgeon%20allegedly%20let%20his%20teenage%20daughter%20drill%20a%20hole%20in%20a%20patient's%20skull.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Faustrian-surgeon-let-teenage-daughter-drill-hole-in-patients-skull-13203934%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faustrian-surgeon-let-teenage-daughter-drill-hole-in-patients-skull-13203934%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faustrian-surgeon-let-teenage-daughter-drill-hole-in-patients-skull-13203934%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientist%20Claims%20He's%20Found%20%26quot%3BPerfect%20Hiding%20Place%26quot%3B%20For%20Missing%20MH370%20Flight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYears%20after%20its%20disappearance%2C%20an%20Australian%20scientist%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20has%20found%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20hiding%20place%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20missing%20MH370%20plane.%20The%20Malaysian%20Airlines%20flight%2C%20with%20239%20people%20on%20board%2C%20vanished%20from%20radar%20after%20taking%20off%20from%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20in%202014.%20Its%20disappearance%20sparked%20the%20biggest%20search%20in%20aviation%20history%20with%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20jet%20still%20unknown%20to%20this%20day.%20Now%2C%20Tasmanian%20researcher%20Vincent%20Lyne%20has%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20he%20has%20figured%20out%20where%20the%20plane%20is.%20In%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%2C%20Mr%20Lyne%20claimed%20that%20the%20plane%20was%20deliberately%20ploughed%20deep%20into%20the%20Broken%20Ridge%20-%20a%2020%2C000-foot-deep%20hole%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20work%20changes%20the%20narrative%20of%20MH370's%20disappearance%20from%20one%20of%20no-blame%2C%20fuel-starvation%20at%20the%207th%20arc%2C%20high-speed%20dive%2C%20to%20a%20mastermind%20pilot%20almost%20executing%20an%20incredible%20perfect-disappearance%20in%20the%20Southern%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researcher%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20it%20would%20have%20worked%20were%20it%20not%20for%20MH370%20ploughing%20its%20right%20wing%20through%20a%20wave%2C%20and%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20regular%20interrogation%20satellite%20communications%20by%20Inmarsat%20-%20a%20brilliant%20discovery%20also%20announced%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Navigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7231166380627148800%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22501%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lyne%2C%20who%20works%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Tasmania's%20Institute%20for%20Marine%20and%20Antarctic%20Studies%2C%20further%20said%20that%20damage%20to%20the%20plane's%20wings%2C%20flaps%20and%20flaperon%20suggest%20it%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontrolled%20ditching%26quot%3B%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20Captain%20Chesley%20%26quot%3BSully%26quot%3B%20Sullenberger%20on%20the%20Hudson%20River%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20justifies%20beyond%20doubt%20the%20original%20claim%2C%20based%20on%20brilliant%2C%20skilled%2C%20and%20very%20careful%20debris-damage%20analyses%2C%20by%20decorated%20ex-Chief%20Canadian%20Air-crash%20Investigator%20Larry%20Vance%2C%20that%20MH370%20had%20fuel%20and%20running%20engines%20when%20it%20underwent%20a%20masterful%20'controlled%20ditching'%20and%20not%20a%20high-speed%20fuel-starved%20crash%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lyne%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researcher%20stated%20that%20MH370%20is%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20longitude%20of%20Penang%20airport%20(the%20runway%20no%20less)%20intersects%20the%20Pilot-in-Command%20home%20simulator%20track%20discovered%20and%20discarded%20by%20the%20FBI%20and%20officials%20as%20'irrelevant.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmysterious-woman-linked-to-arrest-of-telegram-ceo-called-mossad-agent-all-about-juli-vavilova-6420329%5C%22%3EMysterious%20Woman%20Linked%20To%20Arrest%20Of%20Telegram%20CEO%2C%20Called%20Mossad%20Agent%3A%20All%20About%20Juli%20Vavilova%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20pre-meditated%20iconic%20location%20harbors%20a%20very%20deep%206000m%20hole%20at%20the%20eastern%20end%20of%20the%20Broken%20Ridge%20within%20a%20very%20rugged%20and%20dangerous%20ocean%20environment%20renowned%20for%20its%20wild%20fisheries%20and%20new%20deep-water%20species.%20With%20narrow%20steep%20sides%2C%20surrounded%20by%20massive%20ridges%20and%20other%20deep%20holes%2C%20it%20is%20filled%20with%20fine%20sediments%20-%20a%20perfect%20'hiding'%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lyne%20continued%2C%20adding%20the%20area%20needs%20to%20be%20verified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20priority.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it%20will%20be%20searched%20or%20not%20is%20up%20to%20officials%20and%20search%20companies%2C%20but%20as%20far%20as%20science%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20know%20why%20the%20previous%20searches%20failed%20and%20likewise%20science%20unmistakably%20points%20to%20where%20MH370%20lies.%20In%20short%2C%20the%20MH370%20mystery%20has%20been%20comprehensively%20solved%20in%20science!%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20flight%20MH370%20with%20227%20passengers%20and%2012%20crew%20members%20on%20board%20disappeared%20after%20leaving%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20Airport%20in%20southern%20Malaysia%20en%20route%20to%20Beijing%2C%20China%2C%20on%20March%208%2C%202014.%20%C2%A0A%20nearly%20three-year%20search%20covering%20120%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20found%20hardly%20any%20trace%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20with%20only%20some%20pieces%20of%20debris%20picked%20up.%20Despite%20the%20largest%20search%20in%20aviation%20history%2C%20the%20plane%20has%20never%20been%20found%20and%20the%20operation%20was%20suspended%20in%20January%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724734260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Fg6haansk_malaysia-airline-mh370_625x300_25_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fperfect-hiding-place-australian-scientist-says-hes-found-where-missing-mh370-plane-is-6426391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Years%20after%20its%20disappearance%2C%20an%20Australian%20scientist%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20has%20found%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20hiding%20place%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20missing%20MH370%20plane.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fperfect-hiding-place-australian-scientist-says-hes-found-where-missing-mh370-plane-is-6426391%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telegram%20Founder's%20Arrest%20And%20Its%20Widespread%20Implications%20For%20Tech%20Giants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pavel%20Durov%20arrived%20in%20France%20on%20his%20private%20jet%20last%20Saturday%2C%20he%20was%20greeted%20by%20police%20who%20promptly%20arrested%20him.%20As%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20direct%20messaging%20platform%20Telegram%2C%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20facilitating%20the%20widespread%20crimes%20committed%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%2C%20a%20French%20judge%20extended%20Durov's%20initial%20period%20of%20detention%2C%20allowing%20police%20to%20detain%20him%20for%20up%20to%2096%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelegram%20has%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20against%20Durov.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp8ne8r1yy0o%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20company%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20absurd%20to%20claim%20that%20a%20platform%20or%20its%20owner%20are%20responsible%20for%20abuse%20of%20that%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20may%20have%20far-reaching%20international%20implications%2C%20not%20just%20for%20Telegram%20but%20for%20other%20global%20technology%20giants%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Pavel%20Durov%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Russia%20in%201984%2C%20Pavel%20Durov%20also%20has%20French%20citizenship.%20This%20might%20explain%20why%20he%20felt%20free%20to%20travel%20despite%20his%20app's%20role%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6158437%2Ftelegram-russia-ukraine-information-war%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20Russia-Ukraine%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20widespread%20use%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F27007298%3Fseq%3D1%5C%22%3Eextremist%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2111.13530%5C%22%3Ecriminals%20more%20generally%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDurov%20started%20an%20earlier%20social%20media%20site%2C%20VKontakte%2C%20in%202006%2C%20which%20remains%20very%20popular%20in%20Russia.%20However%2C%20a%20dispute%20with%20how%20the%20new%20owners%20of%20the%20site%20were%20operating%20led%20to%20him%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fmedia%2F2014%2Fapr%2F02%2Ffounder-pavel-durov-leaves-russian-social-network-site-vkontakte%5C%22%3Eleaving%20the%20company%20in%202014%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20shortly%20before%20this%20that%20Durov%20created%20Telegram.%20This%20platform%20provides%20both%20the%20means%20for%20communication%20and%20exchange%20as%20well%20as%20the%20protection%20of%20encryption%20that%20makes%20crimes%20harder%20to%20track%20and%20tackle%20than%20ever%20before.%20But%20that%20same%20protection%20also%20enables%20people%20to%20resist%20authoritarian%20governments%20that%20seek%20to%20prevent%20dissent%20or%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDurov%20also%20has%20connections%20with%20famed%20tech%20figures%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20enjoys%20broad%20support%20in%20the%20vocally%20libertarian%20tech%20community.%20But%20his%20platform%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F1369118X.2021.1933562%5C%22%3Elegal%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20even%20in%20his%20birth%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20odd%20target%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavel%20Durov%20is%20in%20some%20ways%20an%20odd%20target%20for%20French%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta's%20WhatsApp%20messenger%20app%20is%20also%20encrypted%20and%20boasts%20three%20times%20as%20many%20users%2C%20while%20X's%20provocations%20for%20hate%20speech%20and%20other%20problematic%20content%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.isi.edu%2Fnews%2F55932%2Fnew-twitter-now-with-more-hate%2F%5C%22%3Eunrepentantly%20public%20and%20increasingly%20widespread%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20no%20suggestion%20that%20Durov%20himself%20was%20engaged%20with%20making%20any%20illegal%20content.%20Instead%2C%20he%20is%20accused%20of%20indirectly%20facilitating%20illegal%20content%20by%20maintaining%20the%20app%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Durov's%20unique%20background%20might%20go%20some%20way%20to%20suggest%20why%20he%20was%20taken%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20major%20tech%20players%2C%20he%20lacks%20US%20citizenship.%20He%20hails%20from%20a%20country%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fkremlin-tightens-control-over-russians-online-lives-threatening-domestic-freedoms-and-the-global-internet-182020%5C%22%3Echequered%20past%20of%20internet%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20and%20a%20diminished%20diplomatic%20standing%20globally%20thanks%20to%20its%20war%20against%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20app%20is%20large%20enough%20to%20be%20a%20global%20presence.%20But%20simultaneously%20it%20is%20not%20large%20enough%20to%20have%20the%20limitless%20legal%20resources%20of%20major%20players%20such%20as%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombined%2C%20these%20factors%20make%20him%20a%20more%20accessible%20target%20to%20test%20the%20enforcement%20of%20expanding%20regulatory%20frameworks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20question%20of%20moderation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDurov's%20arrest%20marks%20another%20act%20in%20the%20often%20confusing%20and%20contradictory%20negotiation%20of%20how%20much%20responsibility%20platforms%20shoulder%20for%20the%20content%20on%20their%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20platforms%2C%20which%20include%20direct%20messaging%20platforms%20such%20as%20Telegram%20and%20WhatsApp%20but%20also%20broader%20services%20such%20as%20those%20offered%20by%20Meta's%20Facebook%20and%20Musk's%20X%2C%20operate%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20they%20contend%20with%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20legal%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20any%20restriction%20put%20on%20a%20platform%20ultimately%20affects%20its%20services%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiley.com%2Fen-us%2FRegulating%2BPlatforms-p-9781509537082%5C%22%3Eeverywhere%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20complicating%20and%20frequently%20preventing%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20side%2C%20there%20is%20a%20push%20to%20either%20hold%20the%20platforms%20responsible%20for%20illegal%20content%20or%20to%20provide%20details%20on%20the%20users%20who%20post%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Russia%2C%20Telegram%20itself%20was%20under%20pressure%20to%20provide%20names%20of%20protesters%20organising%20through%20its%20app%20to%20protest%20the%20war%20against%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20freedom%20of%20speech%20advocates%20have%20fought%20against%20users%20being%20banned%20from%20platforms.%20Meanwhile%2C%20political%20commentators%20cry%20foul%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Ccensored%E2%80%9D%20for%20their%20political%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20contradictions%20make%20regulation%20difficult%20to%20craft%2C%20while%20the%20platforms'%20global%20nature%20makes%20enforcement%20a%20daunting%20challenge.%20This%20challenge%20tends%20to%20play%20in%20platforms'%20favour%2C%20as%20they%20can%20exercise%20a%20relatively%20strong%20sense%20of%20platform%20sovereignty%20in%20how%20they%20decide%20to%20operate%20and%20develop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20complications%20can%20obscure%20the%20ways%20platforms%20can%20operate%20directly%20as%20deliberate%20influencers%20of%20public%20opinion%20and%20even%20publishers%20of%20their%20own%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20one%20example%2C%20both%20Google%20and%20Facebook%20took%20advantage%20of%20their%20central%20place%20in%20the%20information%20economy%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1177%2F14614448231166057%5C%22%3Eadvertise%20politically%20orientated%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20resist%20the%20development%20and%20implementation%20of%20Australia's%20News%20Media%20Bargaining%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platforms'%20construction%20also%20directly%20influences%20what%20content%20can%20appear%20and%20what%20content%20is%20recommended%20%E2%80%93%20and%20hate%20speech%20can%20mark%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsearch.informit.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.3316%2FINFORMIT.790571095083969%5C%22%3Ean%20opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20clicks%20and%20screen%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20pressure%20is%20increasing%20to%20hold%20platforms%20responsible%20for%20how%20they%20moderate%20their%20users%20and%20content.%20In%20Europe%2C%20recent%20regulations%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2Fnews%2Fen%2Fpress-room%2F20240308IPR19014%2Fmedia-freedom-act-a-new-bill-to-protect-eu-journalists-and-press-freedom%5C%22%3Ethe%20Media%20Freedom%20Act%3C%2Fa