0platforms.%20Some%20fans%20even%20believe%20it%20surpasses%20'Stree%202'.%20This%20debate%20has%20sparked%20discussions%20among%20enthusiasts%20of%20the%20Maddock%20supernatural%20universe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmunjya-ott-release-sparks-stree-2-v%2Fs-munjya-debate-fans-say-this-is-the-best-film-in-the-supernatural-universe%2Farticleshow%2F112822099.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNuts%20And%20Bolts%20Were%20Rusted%26quot%3B%3A%20Why%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Statue%20Collapsed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20contractor%20of%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20statue%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Sindhudurg%20which%20collapsed%20on%20Monday%20just%20eight%20months%20since%20it%20was%20inaugurated.%20The%20statue%20was%20unveiled%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20December%204%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20against%20contractor%20Jaydeep%20Apte%20and%20structural%20consultant%20Chetan%20Patil%20under%20several%20sections%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS).%20The%20charges%20include%20collusion%2C%20fraud%2C%20and%20endangering%20public%20safety.%20The%20FIR%20follows%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20(PWD)%2C%20which%20claims%20the%20statue's%20construction%20was%20of%20poor%20quality%2C%20and%20the%20nuts%20and%20bolts%20used%20in%20the%20structure%20were%20found%20to%20be%20rusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20citizens%20and%20tourists%20had%20previously%20expressed%20their%20concerns%20about%20the%20statue's%20deteriorating%20condition.%20Despite%20these%20warnings%2C%20including%20an%20alert%20from%20the%20assistant%20engineer%20of%20the%20Malvan%20division%20of%20the%20PWD%20on%20August%2020%2C%20no%20preventive%20action%20was%20taken.%20The%20PWD%20stated%20that%20the%20rusting%20nuts%20and%20bolts%20posed%20a%20risk%20to%20the%20statue's%20stability%2C%20yet%20the%20warnings%20were%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20steel%20used%20in%20making%20of%20the%20statue%20had%20started%20rusting.%20The%20PWD%20had%20already%20written%20to%20Navy%20officials%20informing%20them%20about%20the%20statue%20catching%20rust%20and%20requested%20them%20to%20take%20appropriate%20steps%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sindhudurg%20guardian%20minister%20Ravindra%20Chavan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20on%20the%20statue%20began%20on%20September%208%2C%20with%20the%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20which%20has%20no%20expertise%20in%20statue%20construction%2C%20being%20tasked%20with%20erecting%20the%20statue%20and%20its%20pedestal.%20The%20statue%20was%20unveiled%20on%20Navy%20Day%20on%20December%204%2C%20at%20Rajkot%20Fort%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20presiding%20over%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20acknowledged%20the%20incident%20and%20attributed%20the%20collapse%20to%20strong%20winds%2C%20claiming%20they%20were%20blowing%20at%20a%20speed%20of%2045%20km%20per%20hour%20at%20the%20time.%20However%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20criticised%20the%20government%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724727000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2vigivv_shivaji-maharaj-statue_625x300_27_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnuts-and-bolts-were-rusted-why-chhatrapati-shivaji-statue-collapsed-6425955%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20contractor%20of%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20statue%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Sindhudurg%20which%20collapsed%20on%20Monday%20just%20eight%20months%20since%20it%20was%20inaugurated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22ht