C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Horizon's%20Lord%20sniper%20rifle%20is%20on%20display%20in%20front%20of%20a%20graphic%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20flag.%3Cp%3EArmyInform%2FMinistry%20of%20Defense%20of%20Ukraine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMilitary%20snipers%20are%20known%20to%20engage%20targets%20with%20extreme%20accuracy%20from%20impressively%20long%20distances.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20longest-distance%20sniper%20kills%20were%20fired%20from%20distances%20as%20far%20as%20one%20to%20two%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Ukrainian%20sniper%20broke%20the%20record%20last%20November%2C%20shooting%20a%20Russian%20soldier%20from%202.36%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20military%20sniper%20makes%20an%20accurate%20shot%20from%20an%20extremely%20long%20distance%2C%20they%20need%20more%20than%20a%20spotter%20and%20a%20rangefinder.%20They%20need%20to%20take%20into%20account%20things%20such%20as%20wind%20direction%2C%20wind%20speed%2C%20air%20density%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Earth's%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20all%20that%2C%20they%20might%20be%20making%20those%20calculations%20while%20enemy%20troops%20are%20actively%20trying%20to%20find%20and%20kill%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20all%20that%20wasn't%20impressive%20enough%2C%20the%20top%20five%20longest-distance%20confirmed%20sniper%20kills%20all%20came%20from%20shots%20fired%20more%20than%20a%20mile%20away%2C%20with%20the%20top%20two%20coming%20in%20from%20more%20than%20two%20miles%20away.%20Since%20the%20average%20human%20with%20an%20unobstructed%20view%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howitworksdaily.com%2Fwhat-is-the-maximum-distance-the-human-eye-can-see-if-unobstructed-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecan%20only%20see%202.9%20miles%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20curvature%20of%20the%20Earth%20cuts%20off%20their%20view%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20the%20enemy%20neither%20saw%20nor%20heard%20the%20bullet%20coming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20top%20five%20spots%20on%20the%20list%20of%20longest-distance%20sniper%20kills%20went%20largely%20unchanged%20starting%20in%202017%20until%20Russia%20gave%20Ukrainian%20snipers%20the%20opportunity%20to%20join%20the%20list%20%E2%80%94%20which%20they%20did.%20Twice.%20Here's%20the%20latest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e70fceba-19aa-4a19-bc4a-1d4e6d01e872%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Viacheslav%20Kovalskyi%2C%20Ukraine%3A%202.36%20miles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20Viacheslav%20Kovalskyi%2C%20a%2058-year-old%20former%20businessman%20and%20now%20a%20sniper%20with%20the%20counterintelligence%20unit%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FServiceSsu%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ServiceSsu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20his%20his%20Horizon's%20Lord%20rifle.%3Cbr%3EHe%20broke%20the%20world%20sniping%20record%20by%20hitting%20a%20russian%20occupier%20at%20a%20distance%20of%203800%20meters.%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FotYzjwZTh9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FotYzjwZTh9%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Defense%20of%20Ukraine%20(%40DefenceU)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDefenceU%2Fstatus%2F1732759885715009673%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20shooters%20on%20this%20list%20go%20unnamed%2C%2058-year-old%20Viacheslav%20Kovalskyi%20is%20proud%20to%20be%20known%20for%20dropping%20a%20Russian%20officer.%20An%20award-winning%2C%20long-distance%20competitive%20shooter%20before%20the%202022%20Russian%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20he%20signed%20up%20as%20a%20sniper%20t