l%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-2-1724335335.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Medini%20Homestay%20in%20Bokakhat%2C%20Assam%2C%20is%20a%20sustainable%20retreat%20created%20by%20couple%20Champak%20Deka%20and%20Anna-Louise%20Meynell.%20Over%20six%20years%2C%20they%20have%20transformed%20a%20barren%20patch%20of%20land%20into%20a%20thriving%20green%20oasis%2C%20promoting%20cruelty-free%20silk%20production%20and%20eco-friendly%20practices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362584%2Fmedini-homestay-kaziranga-national-park-assam-sustainable-champak-deka-anna-louise-meynell%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Organise%20Food%20Drives%20in%20India%3F%205-Step%20Guide%20From%20a%20Man%20Providing%203000%20Free%20Meals%20Weekly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20afternoon%2C%20hundreds%20of%20daily-wage%20labourers%20flock%20to%20the%20bustling%20Nahariya%20circle%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20sparing%20some%20time%20for%20lunch%20in%20an%20exhausting%20work%20day.%20There%2C%20they%20meet%20Somnath%20Kashyap%20eagerly%20awaiting%20to%20hand%20over%20their%20share%20of%20%3Cem%3Epuri%20sabzi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(bread%20with%20curry).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20college%20days%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20Somnath%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20journey%20driven%20by%20a%20simple%20yet%20powerful%20realisation%20%E2%80%94%20the%20distressing%20sight%20of%20food%20wastage%20versus%20the%20glaring%20need%20for%20it%20amongst%20the%20underprivileged%20labourers%20in%20his%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20friend%2C%20who%20was%20a%20caterer%2C%20often%20told%20me%20about%20the%20excess%20food%20they%20had%20to%20throw%20away%20after%20weddings%20and%20events.%20One%20night%2C%20he%20called%20me%20to%