y%20facilities%20including%20food%2C%20medicine%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20footwear.%20I%20feel%20grateful%20to%20all%20those%20who%20are%20making%20the%20old%20age%20home%20a%20great%20place%20for%20people%20like%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20initially%2C%20there%20was%20only%20a%20single%20old%20age%20home%20operational%20for%20blind%20people%2C%20in%202003%2C%20the%20trust%20founded%20another%20one%20for%20non-disabled%20elderly%20people%20who%20lost%20their%20children%20in%20the%202001%20Bhuj%20earthquake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20an%20old%20age%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Laljibhai%20saw%20the%20Mandal%20getting%20radical%20acceptance%20from%20the%20Government%20and%20society%20%E2%80%94%20in%202006%2C%20the%20trust%20was%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20National%20Award%20for%20%E2%80%98Creation%20of%20Barrier-free%20Environment%20for%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%E2%80%99%20by%20Dr%C2%A0%20A%20P%20J%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20then%20President%20of%20India%20%E2%80%94%20he%20decided%20to%20extend%20its%20reach%20to%20the%20youth%20and%20young%20children%20too.%20Every%20activity%20at%20the%20trust%20is%20laced%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20agency%20back%20to%20disabled%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20trust%E2%80%99s%20most%20successful%20initiatives%20is%20the%20inclusive%20education%20programme.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20unique%20school%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333887%2Fsangopita-shelter-home-disabled-children-cerebral-palsy-autism-adhd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20with%20various%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20visual%2C%20intellectual%2C%20hearing%2C%20and%20locomotion%20%E2%80%94%20are%20taught%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laljibhai%20explains.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20programme%20ensures%20that%20these%20students%20are%20included%20in%20the%20mainstream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5