the%20overall%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20more%20time%20for%20herself%2C%20she%20completely%20cut%20off%20from%20social%20media%20and%20social%20engagements%20during%20the%20last%20seven%20months%20of%20training.%20This%20simple%20change%20saved%20her%20almost%20four%20hours%20every%20day%20and%20she%20slept%20at%208%3A30%20pm%20with%20her%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPractice%20intensified%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months.%20Tanvi%20took%20a%20break%20from%20work%20two%20months%20before%20the%20challenge%20and%20focused%20only%20on%20practice.%20She%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F208604%2Findia-record-para-swimmer-satendra-singh-lohia-first-asian-catalina-channel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswim%20for%20eight%20hours%20daily%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eat%20well%2C%20rest%20and%20recover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20month%20before%20the%20actual%20attempt%2C%20Tanvi%20and%20her%20family%20went%20to%20Dover%2C%20UK%20to%20practise%20on%20the%20beach.%20Swimming%20in%20the%20exact%20same%20conditions%20helped%20the%20swimmer%E2%80%99s%20body%20get%20used%20to%20the%20cold%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Never%20thought%20of%20giving%20up%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED-day%3A%2029%20June%2C%202024%2C%203%3A30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20started%20the%20%E2%80%98Mount%20Everest%20of%20Swimming%E2%80%99%20from%20Dover.%20In%20a%20boat%20following%20her%20were%20two%20pilots%2C%20an%20observer%20from%20the%20Channel%20Swimming%20Association%2C%20her%20coach%2C%20husband%2C%20and%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20father%20who%20was%20unwilling%20to%20let%20his%20daughter%20take%20such%20a%20big%20risk%20was%20now%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader.%20At%2064%2C%20he%20had%20to%20wage%20a%20battle%20to%20be%20allowed%20on%20the%20boat.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20usually%20don%E2%80%99t%20allow%20people%20above%2060%20on%20the%20boat%