s%20very%20painful%3B%20I%20almost%20felt%20a%20shock%2C%20an%20electric%20current%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20my%20body%20to%20move%20for%20almost%2020%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20swimming%20for%20nearly%2011%20to%2012%20hours%2C%20the%20weather%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%2C%20with%20high%20tides%20and%20strong%20currents%20making%20progress%20nearly%20impossible.%20Despite%20her%20continuous%20efforts%2C%20Tanvi%20found%20herself%20stuck%20in%20place.%20The%20observer%20on%20her%20support%20boat%20cautioned%20that%20crossing%20the%20channel%20would%20be%20difficult%20under%20such%20conditions.%20This%20treacherous%20region%20of%20the%20English%20Channel%20is%20notoriously%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98swimmer%E2%80%99s%20grave%E2%80%99%20due%20to%20its%20unforgiving%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20three%20hours%2C%20Tanvi%20was%20trapped%20in%20these%20relentless%20currents%2C%20her%20resilience%20tested%20to%20the%20limit.%20The%20situation%20grew%20even%20more%20daunting%20as%20three%20of%20her%20fellow%20swimmers%20were%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20attempts%20due%20to%20the%20worsening%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20waves%20were%20two%20to%20three%20metres%20in%20height%20and%20pulled%20you%20back%20to%20England.%20I%20was%20trapped%20in%20this%20and%20had%20to%20swim%20an%20extra%2010%20kilometres%20to%20reach%20the%20French%20coast%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Tanvi%20pressed%20on%20and%20covered%20the%20additional%2010%20kilometres%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20weather.%20When%20the%20observer%20asked%20if%20she%20wished%20to%20continue%2C%20it%20was%20an%20emphatic%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20actually%20wanted%20to%20give%20up.%20I%20had%20vomited%20and%20had%20zero%20energy.%20It%20was%20thanks%20to%20my%20coach%E2%80%99s%20training%20that%20I%20was%20mentally%20fit%20to%20continue.%20He%20had%20told%20me%20that%20it%20is%20on%20days%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20training%20are%20the%20days%20that%20you%20must%20show%20up.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20when%20your%20hands%20and%20legs%20reach%20their%20breaking%20point%2C%20you%20will%20feel%20like%20giving%20up.%20But%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20up!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20her%20morale%2C%20her%20husband%20showed%20her%20a%20video%20of%20their%20children%20and%20the%20coach%20showed%20her%20the%20Indian%20flag.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20swim%20for%20my%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9RsgjvuVZA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%40swimwithtanvi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20risk%20of%20hypothermia%2C%20where%20